g.title: Invariant: Raw %XX sequences converted to bytes; no null bytes (%00).
Invariant: Full filesystem string constructed in scratch buffer.
Invariant: Absolute path; all symlinks, '..', and '.' components resolved.
Invariant: First N bytes of resolved path exactly match document_root.

ul.li: url_decode: Rejects %00 to prevent C-string truncation attacks.
realpath: Essential to resolve symlinks that point outside the root.
strncmp: Verifies the resolved path still begins with the root.
